ckrts (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  v2.0.0
  * Implemented safe_popen() which doesn't invoke a shell
  * Replaced the backup db by a backup command, so we can let the user decide
    how to backup their data
  * Add an example shell script to perform the required encryption/decryption
    operations.
  * Fix leak when clearing the JSON db. We should use json_decref()
  * Fix a few typos and command outputs
  * Added a "save" command so we can save without exiting if needed.
  * Default the config path as per freedesktop standards (XDG_CONFIG_HOME)
  * coverity fixes

 -- Pascal Lalonde <plalonde@overnet.ca>  Sat, 11 Mar 2023 22:02:35 -0500

